In this generation, many young women involved in an unplanned pregnancy. And sometimes this is the reason of having an abortion because being not ready to be a parent.Below are some tips to prevent pregnancy without using condoms.The Safe WeekThe safe period is the best way to prevent pregnancy without a condom. This means you can make love between the 8th day to the 20th day of a woman s menstrual cycle. Here the first day of the period signifies day one of the menstrual cycles.&nbsp;